1) Download & install the firefox addon from http://seleniumhq.org/download/
2) Download the test scripts from github https://github.com/TechNikh/Drulenium
3) Search & Replace "technikh-enter-your-" text accordingly in the scripts
example:
replace technikh-enter-your-site-name with your site name like google
replace technikh-enter-your-user-name with your user name like admin
replace technikh-enter-your-password with your password
4) Open the scripts in your Selenium IDE



Tested in Selenium IDE 1.4.1




Test cases:
1) anonymous-perm-check -> test to make sure anonymous users don't have access to administration pages